The first virtual operator will reach the Czech Republic already this year.
Maybe
Perhaps the mobile phone market in the Czech Republic is mature enough and our operators offer virtually all services as their partners in Western Europe.
There is still something missing - a virtual operator that requires traditional ones to lower the price.
Maybe it won't be long.
The fact that the Czech operators belong to the most expensive in Europe we have already written many times on Mobil.cz.
In the end, he also confirmed ČTU, which pointed out that the price of SMS is higher to us than in the rest of the Union.
