Both with the formal measures and with the non-formal pressure, then it came to the creation of the first virtual operator and to him there were others.
Unfortunately, the Czech regulator organs are launched from one to the other all of the same as a boiling potato.
For our experience we cannot get rid of the feeling that the lack of clarity of skills in these cases makes him more than comfortable.
But we don't throw the sponge.
If the backstage information is correct and the virtual operator will appear very soon from us, the Czech mobile phone market will return to the motorcycle.
